All Auction Items must be valued at at least 1 matic
	-Items can be anything jpeg, bank codes, credit card #s, etc as long as the file is under 2GB
	-The wallet address of the winner will be posted publicly
The Auction page will load 30 results on a single screen
	-no more than 30 auction items can exist at one time
	-past auctions items + buyers will be in a horizontal scroll bar at the bottom of the screen(past 20)
Clicking on an auction Item will open a new tab with all its information as well as a bid button
Must link wallet to website using metamask or portis
User will receive their item on a flash drive via amazon drone
All buyer addresses are stored forever
Auction considered completed after 5 confirmation on the blockchain
Once program is launched everyone has same access
	-there are no admins that can edit the code
		-if there is a bug that's just unfortunate.
Auction site takes 4% of the payment as a fee, must be be paid by the seller in doge coin
When there have been more than 200 auctions, if more than 60% of previous buyers vote to shut down the site, the fees collected will be split between every past buyer
	-button will appear in top left of the screen upon 200 auctions being completed.
